    <div class="aboutme">     
        <h6 style="font-weight: bold">About Black Hole Jumper:</h6>
        <p>I like the idea of "black hole jumper". My life as a human is to explore as many interesting things as possible on Earth. Once I die, I jump into another universe and start a new journey.</p>
    </div>
     <div class="aboutme">     
        <h6 style="font-weight: bold">Bio:</h6>
        <p>Born in China, I am currently studying at Carleton College, MN, USA. Loving to solve problems, I major in computer science and want to use codes to express creativity and achieve funcionality.</p>
